T02D2560:23b-1: de la skyabs su 'gro ba ni mandala dang mchod pa bshams te /
T02D2560:23b-2: bla ma dang sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'
T02D2560:23b-3: la sogs rang gi mdun du dmigs la 'di skad
T02D2560:23b-4: brjod do // sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2560:23b-5: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams mtha' yas pa na
T02D2560:23b-6: bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams
T02D2560:23b-7: cad dang / dam pa'i chos dang /
T02D2560:23b-9: 'phags pa nyan thos kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2560:23b-10: mchod pa'i las bya ba'i phyir yon chab dang /
T02D2560:23b-16: sil snyan la sogs pa dngos su 'byor pa dang /
T02D2560:23b-17: yid kyis sprul te dbul bar bgyi'o //
T02D2560:23b-19: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba sangs rgyas kun gyi
T02D2560:23b-20: gdung rgyun mi 'chad par bgyi pa'i slad du dus
T02D2560:23b-21: 'di nas bzung nas snying po byang chub ma thob
T02D2560:23b-22: kyi bar du yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas
T02D2560:23b-23: rkang gnyis rnams kyi mchog la skyabs su mchi ste
T02D2560:23b-24: / thugs rje chen po dang ldan pa thams cad mkhyen pa /
T02D2560:23b-25: gzigs pa skyes bu'i khyu mchog sku bsam gyis mi khyab pa /
T02D2560:23b-26: bla na med pa'i sku mnga' ba la skyabs su mchi'o //
T02D2560:23b-27: chos 'dod chags dang bral ba la skyabs su mchi ste /
T02D2560:23b-28: bla na med pa de bzhin gshegs pa la mnga' ba /
T02D2560:23b-29: zhi ba chos kyi sku so sor yang dag par rig pa la skyabs su mchi'o //
T02D2560:23b-30: dge 'dun 'dus pa'i gtso bo la skyabs su mchi ste /
T02D2560:23b-31: phyogs bcu'i byang chub sems dpa'i dge 'dun sa chen
T02D2560:23b-32: por chud pa'i phyir mi ldog pa rnams la skyabs
T02D2560:23b-33: su mchi'o zhes lan gsum brjod do //
